definitions.definition: Any vessel with implements designed to move it in arbitrary direction through one or various bodies of water : a boat , ship , sea scooter , or similar vehicle.
Skill in boating , swimming , or other water-related sports.

main_definition: ( countable and uncountable ) Any vessel with implements designed to move it in arbitrary direction through one or various bodies of water : a boat , ship , sea scooter , or similar vehicle.
secondary_definitions: ( uncountable , rare ) Skill in boating , swimming , or other water-related sports.
